name: The Moon in Full Bloom- Brass Earrings
description:
Birds are chirping, flowers are blooming and you are cheery!

Show off the brightness of this season with these gorgeous earrings. The Moon in full Bloom! Made with Vintage ribbed plastic beads and darling little Czech bell flower glass beads. Total length of 1.5 in (3.81cm), including ear wires.

These are absolutely charming!

If you have any questions please contact me and I will be happy to answer them.

Enjoy your Caprichos!

name: Make a Wish Necklace
description:
Have a secret little wish? make it come true!

Vintage inspired antiqued brass necklace with a striking Amethyst nugget drop, accompanied by a stylish cluster of wish charms. A wishbone, shooting star and a teeny glass bead.

The chain measures 18 inches [Default] (45.72cm) plus the approximately .5in x .75in (1.27x1.9cm) rough amethyst nugget and little cluster of .5in (1.27cm) charms and a little glass bead. Length can definitely be accommodated, just contact us!
Every nugget is natural and completely unique, so it may differ slightly from the one photographed.

Whimsical, charming, and sweet.

If you have any questions please contact me and I will be happy to answer them.

Enjoy your Caprichos!
